author: PlayStation
description:
Coming March 4th, 2025 to PlayStation®5. From the creators of the award-winning Age of Empires franchise, Age of Mythology: Retold goes beyond history to a mythical age where gods, monsters, and humans collide. Combining the best elements of the beloved Age of Mythology with modern real-time strategy design and visuals, Retold is an epic and innovative experience for old and new players alike. Secure your domain, command legendary monsters, and call upon the power of the gods to crush your enemies.    

Pre-Order the Premium Edition today and get up-to 5 days of early access! Unleash the full power of the gods with the Premium Edition of Age of Mythology: Retold. Packed with epic content and exclusive rewards, this edition is the ultimate choice for those ready to dominate the mythical battlefield.
